{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.1","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:1","prev_osis_id":"Num.035.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.036.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">D\u00e9fense aux filles qui h\u00e9ritent de se marier hors de leurs tribus<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-13: cf. No 27:1-11. Jos 17:3, 4.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Les chefs de la famille de Galaad, fils de Makir, fils de Manass\u00e9, d\u2019entre les familles des fils de Joseph, s\u2019approch\u00e8rent et parl\u00e8rent devant Mo\u00efse et devant les princes, chefs de famille des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.2","name":"Nombres 36:2","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.35.34","name":"Nombres 35:34","id":"fra-LSG:Num.35.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.2","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:2","prev_osis_id":"Num.036.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.036.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Ils dirent: L\u2019\u00c9ternel a ordonn\u00e9 \u00e0 mon seigneur de donner le pays en h\u00e9ritage par le sort aux enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. Mon seigneur a aussi re\u00e7u de l\u2019\u00c9ternel l\u2019ordre de donner l\u2019h\u00e9ritage de Tselophchad, notre fr\u00e8re, \u00e0 ses filles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.3","name":"Nombres 36:3","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.1","name":"Nombres 36:1","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.3","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:3","prev_osis_id":"Num.036.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.036.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Si elles se marient \u00e0 l\u2019un des fils d\u2019une autre tribu des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, leur h\u00e9ritage sera retranch\u00e9 de l\u2019h\u00e9ritage de nos p\u00e8res et ajout\u00e9 \u00e0 celui de la tribu \u00e0 laquelle elles appartiendront; ainsi sera diminu\u00e9 l\u2019h\u00e9ritage qui nous est \u00e9chu par le sort.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.4","name":"Nombres 36:4","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.2","name":"Nombres 36:2","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.4","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:4","prev_osis_id":"Num.036.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.036.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Et quand viendra le jubil\u00e9 pour les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, leur h\u00e9ritage sera ajout\u00e9 \u00e0 celui de la tribu \u00e0 laquelle elles appartiendront, et il sera retranch\u00e9 de celui de la tribu de nos p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.5","name":"Nombres 36:5","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.3","name":"Nombres 36:3","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.5","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:5","prev_osis_id":"Num.036.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.036.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Mo\u00efse transmit aux enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl les ordres de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Il dit: La tribu des fils de Joseph a raison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.6","name":"Nombres 36:6","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.4","name":"Nombres 36:4","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.6","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:6","prev_osis_id":"Num.036.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.036.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Voici ce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel ordonne au sujet des filles de Tselophchad: elles se marieront \u00e0 qui elles voudront, pourvu qu\u2019elles se marient dans une famille de la tribu de leurs p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.7","name":"Nombres 36:7","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.5","name":"Nombres 36:5","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.7","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:7","prev_osis_id":"Num.036.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.036.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Aucun h\u00e9ritage parmi les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl ne passera d\u2019une tribu \u00e0 une autre tribu, mais les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl s\u2019attacheront chacun \u00e0 l\u2019h\u00e9ritage de la tribu de ses p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.8","name":"Nombres 36:8","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.6","name":"Nombres 36:6","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.8","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:8","prev_osis_id":"Num.036.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.036.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et toute fille, poss\u00e9dant un h\u00e9ritage dans les tribus des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, se mariera \u00e0 quelqu\u2019un d\u2019une famille de la tribu de son p\u00e8re, afin que les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl poss\u00e8dent chacun l\u2019h\u00e9ritage de leurs p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.9","name":"Nombres 36:9","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.7","name":"Nombres 36:7","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.9","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:9","prev_osis_id":"Num.036.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.036.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Aucun h\u00e9ritage ne passera d\u2019une tribu \u00e0 une autre tribu, mais les tribus des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl s\u2019attacheront chacune \u00e0 son h\u00e9ritage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.10","name":"Nombres 36:10","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.8","name":"Nombres 36:8","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.10","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:10","prev_osis_id":"Num.036.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.036.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Les filles de Tselophchad se conform\u00e8rent \u00e0 l\u2019ordre que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait donn\u00e9 \u00e0 Mo\u00efse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.11","name":"Nombres 36:11","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.9","name":"Nombres 36:9","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.11","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:11","prev_osis_id":"Num.036.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.036.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Machla, Thirtsa, Hogla, Milca et Noa, filles de Tselophchad, se mari\u00e8rent aux fils de leurs oncles;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.12","name":"Nombres 36:12","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.10","name":"Nombres 36:10","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.12","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:12","prev_osis_id":"Num.036.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.036.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>elles se mari\u00e8rent dans les familles des fils de Manass\u00e9, fils de Joseph, et leur h\u00e9ritage resta dans la tribu de la famille de leur p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.13","name":"Nombres 36:13","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.11","name":"Nombres 36:11","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.36.13","label":"","reference":"Nombres 36:13","prev_osis_id":"Num.036.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.001.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.36.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Tels sont les commandements et les lois que l\u2019\u00c9ternel donna par Mo\u00efse aux enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, dans les plaines de Moab, pr\u00e8s du Jourdain, vis-\u00e0-vis de J\u00e9richo.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.36","name":"Nombres 36","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.1.1","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.1.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.36.12","name":"Nombres 36:12","id":"fra-LSG:Num.36.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb1e57ec7.91957250');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb1e57ec7.91957250\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb1e57ec7.91957250","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb1e57ec7.91957250'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb1e57ec7.91957250\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}